## DED Mémoriel Filter v0.1.0-alpha

Initial public alpha release of **DED Mémoriel Filter**, a lightweight selective inference wrapper for large language models.

This release includes:

- entropy-based phase detection: D / É / R
- structured abstention mechanism
- CycleMemory prototype
- simulation on TruthfulQA reference setting, N = 817
- OFF / ON ablation results
- technical FAQ
- validation plan for real-logit calibration
- AGPLv3 licensing from this release onward

## Status

Results are preliminary and simulation-based only.  
They do not yet constitute experimental validation on real model logits.

Real-logit GPU calibration is planned as the next validation step.

